  "text": "Implicit Model: In the implicit model, we obtain polynomial time implementations for lex-DFS and general-DFS using O(lg n) bits. For lex-DFS, this is conjectured to be unlikely in ROM as the problem is P-complete [CITATION_1] . In particular, we show the following in Section 5.",
